Fixed a bug which caused a lag when composing messages. Added the option to rejoin a group call you get dropped.
We fixed a bug that occurs when adding a user to a group call. Prior to this fix the user didn t appear on the contact list.
You now have the option to show previous group chat history to new group members.

Improved date and time format for outgoing and incoming messages Added the option to delete your account permanently. Added a Calls tab that gives you access to your call history with the option to wipe it from the device and server. Enabled the upload of multiple photos and videos while sending them. Fixed issue having to do with links and audio files not getting shared via the app.
In this version we fixed a bug related to received video sound playing even after you close the video player.
In this build we improved group admin permissions.
Fixed null message notification bug

Comes with an upgradable 30GB Free storage A.I powered file scanning to reduce chances of your device getting infected with malware In addition to the existing Stealth functionality we added a Teams option including the ability to create and manage groups now allows you to collaborate with others. You are now able to share all types of files Word Excel Pdf PowerPoint etc... . You can hide or show your online Status to your contacts. You can share your individual or group profile. You can share a meeting link with anyone and they can join from their web browser without having to install anything. The application can also be accessed from a web browser Webchat version .
Chat issue fixes
Fixed message notification issue.

Implemented new in app purchases so users can enjoy a free trial prior to purchase. A screen recording notification gets sent to you when your message recipient starts or stops the screen recording of your messages or calls voice or video .

Improved poor connection indicator.

Sending encrypted voice and video messages that self destruct once viewed. works only from iOS to iOS for now . Encrypted Voice call and Video conference with up to 6 participants works only from iOs to iOS for now . Selective Blocking: Instead of a full block you can do a partial block to keep someone from sending you messages or certain file types while allowing others.
